Arch
===

index.html
archives.html ;;all blog entries
404.html      ;;404 error page 
posts/        ;;all post pages here 
images/       ;; all images here


Usgae
===
Add a post:
0. create a well-names page in posts using the post-template.html file
1. update index.html
2. update archives.html
3. done!

add a page:
0. create a page in root dir or any sub-folder, with all relative url right.
1. update index.html